1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely sub-category as the paper deals with semantic segmentation of road driving images using deep learning techniques. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel approach to achieve better performance on a wide range of computing budgets. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with the application of AI techniques for real-time prediction on mobile platforms. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible sub-category as the paper mentions the use of the proposed approach for various kinds of robots. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely sub-category as the paper does not deal with any security or cryptography-related topics.
